Package com.rohitsood.urlybird.client

Interface Summary
DatabaseClient The DatabaseClient interface is used by all types of client.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDatabaseClient Responsible for creating a unique VMID for the client.
DatabaseClientFactory Factory for creating clients.
DatabaseDirectClient Provides direct access to the underlying database file system.
DatabaseNetworkClient Provides access to the database server over a network.
 

Exception Summary
DatabaseServerException A special RuntimeException that signifies an unexpected exception on the database server.
